ZH: 除非明天下雨，否则我们会去爬山。
EN: We will go hiking tomorrow unless it rains.

ZH: 除非你有学习的时间，否则你不能玩手机。
EN: You can't play on your phone unless you have study time.

ZH: 除非我变强壮，否则我不会去打篮球。
EN: I won't play basketball unless I become stronger.

ZH: 除非她请假，否则她不会缺席会议。
EN: She won't be absent from the meeting unless she takes a leave of absence.

ZH: 除非你发誓，否则我不会相信你。
EN: I won't believe you unless you swear.

ZH: 除非他道歉，否则我不会原谅他。
EN: I won't forgive him unless he apologizes.

ZH: 除非今天有紧急情况，否则我们不会改变计划。
EN: We won't change the plan unless there is an emergency today.

ZH: 除非你同意，否则我们不会做任何决定。
EN: We won't make any decisions unless you agree.

ZH: 除非你把作业做完，否则你不能去玩。
EN: You can't go play unless you finish your homework.

ZH: 除非我找到工作，否则我不会搬家。
EN: I won't move unless I find a job.

ZH: 除非我想去，否则我不会参加聚会。
EN: I won't attend the party unless I feel like it.

ZH: 除非你刷牙洗脸，否则你不能吃早餐。
EN: You can't have breakfast unless you brush your teeth and wash your face.

ZH: 除非你尊重别人，否则别人也不会尊重你。
EN: Others won't respect you unless you respect them.

ZH: 除非你节约用水，否则水资源会被浪费。
EN: Water resources will be wasted unless you save water.

ZH: 除非明天天气好，否则野餐计划会取消。
EN: The picnic plan will be canceled unless the weather is good tomorrow.

ZH: 除非他请假，否则他不能缺席考试。
EN: He can't miss the exam unless he takes a leave of absence.

ZH: 除非你爱护宠物，否则不要养宠物。
EN: Don't keep pets unless you take care of them.

ZH: 除非今晚有紧急会议，否则我们会按时下班。
EN: We will leave on time unless there is an emergency meeting tonight.

ZH: 除非你努力工作，否则你达不到自己的目标。
EN: You won't achieve your goals unless you work hard.

ZH: 除非你提醒我，否则我可能会忘记这个重要事件。
EN: I might forget about this important event unless you remind me.
